nodes.text: The wardrobe warehouse was a facility located in the Jedi Temple on Coruscant servicing the needs of the members of the Jedi Order sent on undercover missions. Circa 22 BBY, Jedi Master Taria Damsin and Padawan Ahsoka Tano visited the Warehouse before departing on their Mission to Corellia to properly disguise themselves as tourists on the planet.
